      <lg xml:id="Aink145">
<l>ekkar ñāḻaṟ ciṟiyilaip peruñciṉai</l>
<l>yōtam vāṅkun tuṟaivaṉ</l>
<l>māyōḷ pacalai nīkkiṉa ṉiṉiyē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>The man from the ghat</l>
  <l>Where Ñāḻal trees on the dunes with small leaves [on] big branches </l>
    <l>Curve [because of] floods </l>
        <l>Has removed the pallor of the dark girl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
